- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as reinforcement learning is a subfield of AI. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a potential category as the paper deals with optimizing data transfer in a system (cellular network). 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also possible as the paper involves data transmission and rate improvements.
